BEP-3: Quality tools
Abstract: to set up a series of quality tools (scripts) to ensure the quality of the
code, such as style, test and documentation coverage, efficiency tests.

Available tools
---------------
* pylint, pychecker, pymetrics, pyflakes

Tests
-----
* Have an additional separate module with user-defined tests? (or more global tests)
* Handling bugs: write failing tests. When the bug is solved, the test passes and can be
added to the test suite.

Style
-----
* Style checker (e.g. from brian import * and check all globals)

Miscellaneous ideas
-------------------
* Write a guide for developers
